title: Universal Trimmer Shoulder Strap Harness Weeder Grass Edger Lawn Adjustable Belt
item_description:
Universal Trimmer Shoulder Strap Harness Weeder Grass Edger Lawn Adjustable Belt
Feature:
This for weed eater strap was made of nylon material and high impact polymer attachment was tested to hold 100 lb weights, has a long service life.
Adjustable weed wacker strap, 1.5" strap, 28-35", suitable for most body size.
The string trimmer strap with adapter attachment strap which is fit for less than 6 inch diameter role, compatible with multi head system, most brand's grass trimmer, weedeater, leaf blower, some of shrub trimmers.
The shoulder strap harness for weed trimmer share the weight of the trimmer, leaf blower, multi head system etc., reduce fatigue and soreness of the arm; Rotatable clip provide more flexible.
Lightweight for weed eater sling come with a mesh surface shoulder pad, increase breathable, comfortable and reduce fatigue.
Easy to Install:
Step 1: Expand the interface belt.
Step 2: Adjust the port fits the size of machine.
Step 3: Adjust the shoulder strap length to suit you.
Step 4: Fixed on the machine, ready to use.
